title: Tanakun
description: Tanakun is a fortified city in or bordering the northeastern part of Que. It is mentioned in royal inscriptions of the Assyrian king Shalmaneser III (r. 858-824 BC).

properties.description: The proposed location of Tanakun follows the suggestion that Domuztepe Höyük was the location of this fortified city. The coordinates are the central point of OSM Way Domuztepe Höyük (171207266).
properties.title: Proposed location of Tanakun
